column1: Hey, how are you? I just got back from walking my dog. Do you have any pets?
Oh, I'm sorry to hear that. I have two dogs and a cat. What do you do for fun?
I love to read as well. Do you have any favorite authors or genres?
Science fiction is one of my favorite genres as well! What is your favorite book?
I haven't read that one yet, but I have heard good things about it. What is it about?
That sounds interesting. I will have to check it out. Do you have any favorite authors?
I have never read any of his books, but I have heard good things about him. What is your favorite book of his?
I will have to check them out. I know he wrote a lot of short stories in his youth.
Oh wow, that is a long time ago. He must have been a very talented writer.
Wow, I didn't know that. I know he wrote a lot of poetry.
Yes, he was a very talented poet. He was born in 1942.
Yes, it is. It was published in 1959, but it was so long ago.
Yes, I know. It's a great book. I read it a lot when I was a kid.
I don't really have a favorite book, but I do know that it was published in 1939.
Yes, it is. It was written by James Fenimore Cooper.
It really is! It was published in 1937. It's a classic.
Yes, it is. It was written by James Fenimore Cooper.
It really is! It was published in 1937. It's been a while since I've read it.
I haven't read it in a long time either. I think I'll pick it up again soon.
I'll have to check it out. I've been wanting to read it for a while now.
